Positioner Documentation
========================

Database:
========
See positionerExample for an example ioc. To build this uncomment the module in the Makefile, and uncomment the relevant lines in configure/RELEASE.


Screens:
======

Macros
------
$(mp) = multipostioner PV (normally $(P):MP)
$(p1)..$(p8) = positioner PVs, so $(mp)$(p1) is the first positioner (normally $(p1)=$(M[n]) where the [n]th motor in a device is a positioner)
